# Phase 7 Stage 7.7.a (Doc 72): bundled `.image` artifacts are
# AOT-baked Sexp trees produced by `make bake-images` from the sibling
# `.el` source.  They are git-tracked so that downstream cargo builds
# can `include_bytes!` them without running the baker, but a textual
# diff would be useless — review the `.el` change instead.
*.image binary

# NeLisp's nelisp-sys typed-elisp DSL sources use the `.nl' extension, which
# GitHub Linguist otherwise misclassifies as the unrelated NewLisp language.
# These files are NeLisp (an Emacs Lisp dialect) source -- count them as Emacs Lisp.
*.nl linguist-language=Emacs-Lisp
